21 年评选的「年度国家」是意大利，上榜理由为政治成就。前几年的获奖者包括乌兹别克斯坦（因废除奴隶制而获奖）、哥伦比亚（因促成和平而获奖) 、突尼斯 (因拥抱民主而获奖) 等。 据外媒此前报道，法新社称，美国《时代》杂志 12 月 7 日宣布将乌克兰总统泽连斯基和「乌克兰精神」评为该杂志 2022 年年度人物，以表彰乌克兰在面对俄罗斯「入侵」时展现出的精神。俄罗斯总统新闻秘书、克宫发言人佩斯科夫进行了回应。据俄卫星社 12 月 8 日消息，佩斯科夫回应称，该刊物的判据标准没有跳出泛欧主流意识的范围，带有狭隘和狂热的恐俄特征。《经济学人》把 2022「年度国家」给了乌克兰，称选择「显而易见」（环球网）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-1ed800914c90a35d36eb8f02f46305e6_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/573584835"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I3OjjmKjk4KhhEAMaCDg5NzQ1NjQ1IKTeip0GMAM4YkAXcgk1NzM1ODQ4MzV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1671755323.826453", "card_id": "Q_572694454", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2022 年底将至，大盘还会出现反转吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "大家怎么看？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e01fd9368aff4a238b73f6f298fab3e5_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "47 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/572694454"}}, "attached_info": "ClQI3OjjmKjk4KhhEAMaCDg5NTQ3NzEyIMia8JwGMAA4KkAYcgk1NzI2OTQ0NTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1671755323.8269975", "card_id": "Q_557269308", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 238}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么日漫普遍是黑白的，在他们那发表彩色漫画岂不是很能卷？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-144519785a2ec2beb29cf2e6f52f8014_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "li